{
  "id": "level-3/composition-002",
  "level": 3,
  "name": "two intents with potential conflict but mutually exclusive conditions",
  "description": "Two intents target the same entity but have mutually exclusive conditions (status='active' vs status='archived'). Even though effects might conflict, they can never both apply. No composition findings expected.",
  "input": {
